"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The US military reports another death a day after two of its soldiers were killed in Jordan. Iran responded with attacks in Syria and Jordan, as two ships reportedly exploded in the Strait of Hormuz. Eight people die and dozens are injured as several cities are hit by missile and drone attacks, while Kyiv continues its own assault on Russian infrastructure.\",            \"english_title\": \"US Military Reports Deaths\",            \"translated_version\": \"El ej\u00e9rcito de EE.UU. informa otra muerte un d\u00eda despu\u00e9s de que dos de sus soldados murieran en Jordania. Ir\u00e1n respondi\u00f3 con ataques en Siria y Jordania, y dos barcos explotaron en el Estrecho de Ormuz. Ocho personas mueren y muchas est\u00e1n heridas cuando varias ciudades son atacadas por misiles y drones, mientras Kyiv sigue atacando la infraestructura rusa.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Muertes en el Ej\u00e9rcito de EE.UU.\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Two other young people were injured after a fountain partially collapsed in Salamanca's Ciudad Rodrigo.\",            \"english_title\": \"Fountain Collapse Injures Youths\",            \"translated_version\": \"Dos j\u00f3venes m\u00e1s resultaron heridos despu\u00e9s de que una fuente se derrumbara parcialmente en Ciudad Rodrigo de Salamanca.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Colapso de Fuente Hierye a J\u00f3venes\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The artwork in the capital Oslo was unveiled on Sunday ahead of the 15th anniversary of the attack.\",            \"english_title\": \"Artwork Unveiled in Oslo\",            \"translated_version\": \"La obra de arte en la capital Oslo fue presentada el domingo antes del 15 aniversario del ataque.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Obra de Arte en Oslo\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Wang Jibing is among blue-collar Chinese workers gaining wider attention for their literary works.\",            \"english_title\": \"Chinese Workers Gain Attention\",            \"translated_version\": \"Wang Jibing est\u00e1 entre los trabajadores chinos que est\u00e1n ganando atenci\u00f3n por sus obras literarias.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Trabajadores Chinos Ganan Atenci\u00f3n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The protesters, who are demanding education reforms, are marching despite a police ban.\",            \"english_title\": \"Protesters Demand Education Reforms\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los manifestantes, que piden reformas educativas, est\u00e1n marchando a pesar de una prohibici\u00f3n policial.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Manifestantes Piden Reformas Educativas\"        }    ]}"